9aab92e0-e516-4c98-9499-5f11538d3437,X007,Philippines Flagship,ACTIVE,AEPW,Philippines,Philippines,DRAFT,"The program objective is to develop solution pathways at scale to reduce unmanaged waste and capture value from waste by mobilizing capital in selected Philippines cities. Desired outcome is to reduce the plastic waste pollution in selected Philippines cities by strengthening waste collection, sorting, recycling and proper disposal through co-funding infrastructure, innovation, education, and clean up, by 2026 taking into consideration the Extended Producer Responsibility (EPR) requirements. The Project will focus on collection and sorting of waste. The sorted fractions will then be further processed downstream through recycling operations to improve current recycling rates. The target is to supply high-quality recycling feedstock of at least 50 KTA (Kilo Tonnes per Annum) output volume for market off-take.",The program objective is to develop solution pathways at scale to reduce unmanaged waste and capture value from waste by mobilizing capital in selected Philippines cities.,,,"[""12.40318530245403600"",""122.78317730361327000""]",ESTIMATE,Philippines,,,2024-10-29 09:28:34.98
